ount": 55}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "7 、 8 月份国内去哪旅游性价比高？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-918616f29ec628ca02a19afb2892b049_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "63 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/611301406"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I6a3LvPzQt+k4EAMaCDk4MTI1NTQxIPfdraUGMAA4ZkAKcgk2MTEzMDE0MDZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1691726707.725910", "card_id": "Q_615964266", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 150}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "别人给领导送礼，领导拒收后，对方把礼物放在我这里，我事后把礼物隐蔽地交给了领导，这样的做法对不对？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "别人给烟，我贴上签放在了领导桌上隐蔽的地，事后没提过。 还有别人送礼给领导，领导不要，他放到了我这里，托我给领导 。人走后，我说清了原由，管领导要他的车钥匙放到他车上，但领导没有立刻给我钥匙，就说不要收了。我说也没想太多，领导说那这个... 停顿了很久，我接上了说，下次再给不要了，钥匙在哪 ？ 领导掏出了钥匙，我趁没人时放在了她车上，这事全程对我没有一点好处，反倒出了问题有责任？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/f25303335.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "54 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/615964266"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I6a3LvPzQt+k4EAMaCDk5MTYxMTEzII/YvqYGMAA4vAJAC3IJNjE1OTY0MjY2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1691726707.729330", "card_id": "Q_616184443", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 139}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "美国女子因喝水过多身亡，因「20 分钟内喝下 4 瓶水引发水中毒」，如何解读该现象，该怎样预防水中毒？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "本文转自【海外网】； 海外网 8 月 8 日电据福克斯新闻网 7 日报道，美国印第安纳州一名 35 岁女子近日在度假时，因短时间内喝了过量的水而身亡。 去世女子名叫阿什利·萨默斯。7 月 4 日，她与家人在印第安纳州水库弗里曼湖度假。其家人称，她在 20 分钟内喝下 4 瓶水，随后开始头痛、头晕和脱水，称总是感觉喝不到足够的水。萨默斯之后昏倒在车库，被送往医院后再也没有醒来。 医生表示，萨默斯死于水中毒。她喝下的每瓶水容量为 16 盎司，这几乎是一个人全天的饮水量。女性每日液体摄入量应该为 92 盎司，其中 20% 的液体来自食物。萨默斯的家人表示十分震惊，因为他们第一次了解水中毒。 福克斯新闻网表示，水中毒主要是因人体的水摄入过多而导致低钠血症。人体内的水位上升后，细胞开始肿胀，并由此引发许多健康问题。（海外网 王珊宁）美国女子因喝水过多身亡：20 分钟内喝下 4 瓶水 引发水中毒 _ 阿什利·萨默斯 _ 福克斯 _ 家人"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-bb7695e0c4dffec661f5fb8878f23907_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "52 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/616184443"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I6a3LvPzQt+k4EAMaCDk5MjEwMTUyINmwxqYGMAA46ANADHIJNjE2MTg0NDQzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1691726707.731893", "card_id": "Q_616311228", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 36}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你在山顶或海边看过日出日落吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-a8b06d7dbd5e26666e3361ce47d173e9_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "50 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/616311228"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I6a3LvPzQt+k4EAMaCDk5MjM4MjcxIMeVyaYGMAA4JUANcgk2MTYzMTEyMjh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1691726707.734375", "card_id": "Q_616199899", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 101}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有哪些让你感觉激情澎湃的诗句？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-b36170b17fcd39f7e5293d27ccf77c0f_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "48 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.c